## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

###
## ─── Available Quests ───
###

### View available quests at current town
GET {{host}}/quests/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Active Quests ───
###

### View active/completed quests
GET {{host}}/quests/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Accept Quest ───
###

### Accept a starter quest at Thornhaven
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}

### Accept the wolf pelts quest
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-wolf-pelts"
}

### Accept the chapel pilgrimage quest
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-chapel-pilgrimage"
}

###
## ─── Turn In Quest ───
###

### Turn in a completed quest
POST {{host}}/quests/turn-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}

###
## ─── Abandon Quest ───
###

### Abandon an active quest
POST {{host}}/quests/abandon
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-wolf-pelts"
}

###
## ─── Error Cases ───
###

### Accept quest when not at town — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "saltmere-crab-harvest"
}

### Accept non-existent quest — should fail (404)
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "fake-quest-id"
}

### Turn in quest that's not completed — should fail (400)
POST {{host}}/quests/turn-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}

### Abandon a turned-in quest — should fail (409)
POST {{host}}/quests/abandon
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}

### View available quests when not at town — should fail (400)
GET {{host}}/quests/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
## ─── Workflow: Full Quest Cycle ───
###

### 1. Travel to Thornhaven first
POST {{host}}/travel/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "destinationX": 50,
  "destinationY": 50
}

### 2. Check travel status (wait for arrival)
GET {{host}}/travel/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. View available quests
GET {{host}}/quests/available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Accept the rat problem quest
POST {{host}}/quests/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}

### 5. Check active quests
GET {{host}}/quests/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Kill monsters (progress updates automatically via combat)
POST {{host}}/combat/action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "attack"
}

### 7. Check active quests again (progress should update)
GET {{host}}/quests/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Return to Thornhaven and turn in
POST {{host}}/quests/turn-in
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "questId": "thornhaven-rat-problem"
}
